tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE teleportation_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    person_name VARCHAR(50),
    teleportation_date DATE,
    measurement1 FLOAT,
    measurement2 FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE teleportation_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    source_qubit VARCHAR(50),
    target_qubit VARCHAR(50),
    entangled BIT,
    teleportation_success BIT
);
